Hi I Have An App Called Reader Its A batch File So Heres Da Script
@echo off
title Reader
Color a
echo Hello User, Please To Read A TXT If In Some Reason You Cant Try Out This Program
echo Drag The File Or Put The Path And The File Name With The Extension
set /p input="Here Type In:"
type %input%>nul
if %errorlevel% == 0 echo Done Successfully LOL
if %errorlevel% !==! 0 Echo Done Not Successfully XD (Maybe You Put The Wrong Path Or File Name Or Forgot The Extension)
pause>nul
